OL,5,
OL,6,CG2013FSimon McCoy and Sophie Long
OL,7,Fpresent the final BBC News channel
OL,8,Fprogramme to be broadcast from BBC
OL,9,FTelevision Centre. The programme was
OL,10,Fbased in studio N6 and went out 8.30am
OL,11,F- 1pm. The BBC News at One was the
OL,12,Ffirst domestic news programme to be
OL,13,Fbroadcast from New Broadcasting House.
